# 17D4  Invader fire in progress #
# 17D5  Keyboard byte #
# 17D6  Laser fire in progress #
# 17D8  Laser fire address #
# 17DB  Invader fire address #
# 17DD  Displacement of new frame #
# 18E0  Size of frame #
# 1842  Last Invader to fire #

